race.description: Vote Of Thanks Jenny Searle Handicap (55)
race.comment: ALPINE RAIDER (7) ran a nice race when fresh from a spell last time out, finishing second and beaten only 2 lengths over 1000m at Toowoomba. Needs to be at his best to beat this field but he has the ability to mix it with them. BEE EXACT (4) showed good early speed then led into the straight last start before fighting on to finish third, beaten a long neck, over 1350m at Ipswich. Will push forward and is among the chances. SONIC ARROW (14) could only manage sixth two runs back then improved last start but just found a couple better over 1000m at Dalby, beaten 3.5 lengths. Capable of featuring prominently. RESOLUTE LADY (9) rounds out the selections in an open affair.
